WEBVTT

00:00:35.320 --> 00:00:45.400
Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:00:58.880 --> 00:00:59.759
Sister Yuling

00:01:03.520 --> 00:01:04.480
You are so kind.

00:01:05.439 --> 00:01:07.319
Teaching us to read and write,

00:01:07.319 --> 00:01:08.879
to do math and sing,

00:01:09.239 --> 00:01:10.799
and even washing our clothes

00:01:10.799 --> 00:01:11.680
and cutting our hair.

00:01:11.920 --> 00:01:12.920
I heard

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:13.920
that those teachers

00:01:13.920 --> 00:01:15.640
are all college students

00:01:15.640 --> 00:01:17.159
from big cities like Beijing and Shanghai.

00:01:17.760 --> 00:01:19.560
They gave up such good places

00:01:20.079 --> 00:01:21.359
to come here and help us.

00:01:21.439 --> 00:01:22.280
Don't say that.

00:01:22.680 --> 00:01:24.480
Seeing you study in peace

00:01:24.480 --> 00:01:25.480
and grow up healthy

00:01:25.840 --> 00:01:27.280
makes us happier than anything.

00:01:27.560 --> 00:01:28.359
By the way,

00:01:29.079 --> 00:01:31.239
do you know the story behind Brother Gao Yuan's harmonica?

00:01:31.640 --> 00:01:32.760
Last time,

00:01:32.760 --> 00:01:33.959
after he was injured building the road,

00:01:34.439 --> 00:01:35.680
he couldn't find it anywhere.

00:01:36.319 --> 00:01:38.920
I saw him go look under the collapsed cliff several times.

00:01:39.760 --> 00:01:41.519
Is this harmonica

00:01:41.519 --> 00:01:42.560
very important to him?

00:01:42.959 --> 00:01:44.159
It's his keepsake.

00:01:45.359 --> 00:01:46.640
When he first graduated from college

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:48.000
and joined the army,

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:49.319
he was still a rookie.

00:01:49.879 --> 00:01:51.040
On the way into Tibet,

00:01:51.159 --> 00:01:53.239
his old squad leader died

00:01:53.239 --> 00:01:54.560
protecting him.

00:01:54.640 --> 00:01:55.560
That harmonica

00:01:55.840 --> 00:01:58.120
is the only thing his old squad leader left him.

00:01:59.079 --> 00:01:59.599
Later on,

00:01:59.599 --> 00:02:01.239
as his comrades fell one by one,

00:02:01.560 --> 00:02:03.319
Gao Yuan played the harmonica

00:02:03.319 --> 00:02:05.159
more and more often.

00:02:06.879 --> 00:02:07.680
Meiduo.

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:08.199
Hmm?

00:02:08.199 --> 00:02:09.599
Don't be fooled by his mouth,

00:02:09.599 --> 00:02:10.719
which seems locked shut.

00:02:11.080 --> 00:02:12.599
But the fire in his heart

00:02:12.599 --> 00:02:14.120
burns fiercer than anyone's.

00:02:14.240 --> 00:02:15.719
His feelings are truer than anyone's.

00:02:15.919 --> 00:02:17.759
For the brothers who never returned,

00:02:17.879 --> 00:02:19.479
and for our Tibetan compatriots

00:02:19.479 --> 00:02:20.759
to live a good life,

00:02:21.039 --> 00:02:22.280
for six years now,

00:02:22.280 --> 00:02:23.800
his home is right there,

00:02:23.879 --> 00:02:25.520
yet he hasn't gone back once.

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:27.439
The home in his heart

00:02:28.360 --> 00:02:30.520
is no longer that little courtyard on Xianyang Yuan.

00:02:34.319 --> 00:02:35.800
Classmates,

00:02:35.800 --> 00:02:37.639
today we won't teach reading

00:02:37.960 --> 00:02:39.280
or arithmetic.

00:02:40.120 --> 00:02:43.000
Today, we'll discuss a word:

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:44.120
"ideal."

00:02:47.879 --> 00:02:49.280
Teacher,

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:51.520
what is an ideal?

00:02:53.520 --> 00:02:54.840
An ideal is

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:56.919
a beautiful, long-term goal or state

00:02:56.919 --> 00:02:58.719
that people yearn for in their hearts

00:02:58.719 --> 00:03:00.879
and strive to achieve.

00:03:00.879 --> 00:03:01.919
In simple terms,

00:03:02.680 --> 00:03:03.879
an ideal is something

00:03:04.120 --> 00:03:07.719
a person would give their life to do.

00:03:10.960 --> 00:03:12.039
Gesang Deji,

00:03:15.240 --> 00:03:17.479
take Deji for example.

00:03:17.479 --> 00:03:20.039
Why did you hide the acupuncture kit yesterday?

00:03:20.319 --> 00:03:21.479
Were you thinking that

00:03:21.479 --> 00:03:22.680
someday,

00:03:22.680 --> 00:03:24.080
you too would heal and save people?

00:03:24.479 --> 00:03:25.280
Mm-hmm.

00:03:25.280 --> 00:03:26.039
Yes.

00:03:26.039 --> 00:03:27.360
That is your ideal.

00:03:28.199 --> 00:03:28.960
Meiduo,

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:31.520
tell us,

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:32.719
what is your ideal?

00:03:33.280 --> 00:03:35.800
Something I'd give my life to do...

00:03:35.800 --> 00:03:37.080
was to escape with my sister.

00:03:37.560 --> 00:03:39.879
But does that count as an ideal?

00:03:42.120 --> 00:03:43.639
My...

00:03:43.759 --> 00:03:45.199
My ideal

00:03:45.199 --> 00:03:45.879
is...

00:03:46.560 --> 00:03:47.360
It's okay.

00:03:50.520 --> 00:03:51.439
Classmates,

00:03:51.439 --> 00:03:54.240
An ideal isn't something you have in a day or two,

00:03:54.360 --> 00:03:56.039
nor is it unchanging.

00:03:56.919 --> 00:03:59.680
I hope you all can have your own ideals

00:03:59.919 --> 00:04:01.240
and strive for them.

00:04:11.240 --> 00:04:12.719
Truly lowborn to the core.

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:14.479
You'd pick up something so filthy.

00:04:14.560 --> 00:04:15.400
Exactly.

00:04:15.400 --> 00:04:16.560
Like an animal,

00:04:16.759 --> 00:04:17.839
not even minding the dirt.

00:04:18.360 --> 00:04:20.800
No wonder you're born from household serfs.

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:23.040
How dare you talk about my sister like that!

00:04:26.720 --> 00:04:27.959
What are you all doing?

00:04:34.519 --> 00:04:35.879
Apologize to classmate Meiduo.

00:04:36.319 --> 00:04:37.879
Why should we?

00:04:43.959 --> 00:04:44.759
Meiduo,

00:04:45.319 --> 00:04:46.600
it fell on the dirty ground.

00:04:46.959 --> 00:04:47.759
Eat my portion.

00:04:48.079 --> 00:04:49.079
Give me yours to eat.

00:04:50.920 --> 00:04:51.720
Dirty?

00:04:52.720 --> 00:04:53.519
I don't think so.

00:04:54.839 --> 00:04:57.560
I won't feel ashamed for eating a dirty pancake.

00:04:59.720 --> 00:05:02.000
I'm ashamed of your condescension.

00:05:02.560 --> 00:05:04.240
You feed on the blood and flesh of serfs,

00:05:04.759 --> 00:05:07.199
yet you even mock them for eating a dirty pancake.

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:08.839
What's ingrained in your bones

00:05:09.560 --> 00:05:11.959
is a cruelty and indifference toward your own kind you can't wash away.

00:05:12.160 --> 00:05:13.680
You are the ones who are truly dirty,

00:05:14.040 --> 00:05:15.879
the lowborn ones you speak of.

00:05:25.360 --> 00:05:26.160
Meiduo.

00:05:36.959 --> 00:05:37.759
Meiduo.

00:05:39.120 --> 00:05:40.439
Are you okay?

00:05:40.439 --> 00:05:42.000
Brother Gao Yuan.

00:05:42.759 --> 00:05:44.000
In your mind,

00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:45.639
am I that fragile?

00:05:49.120 --> 00:05:50.040
Then why

00:05:51.000 --> 00:05:52.120
did you come out here?

00:05:53.439 --> 00:05:54.959
I just suddenly understood

00:05:55.959 --> 00:05:57.879
what it means to do something with all your might,

00:06:00.680 --> 00:06:01.720
what an ideal is.

00:06:09.319 --> 00:06:10.120
Fellow classmates,

00:06:10.120 --> 00:06:11.120
welcome.

00:06:11.560 --> 00:06:14.480
Today is our Life Ideals Discussion Meeting.

00:06:15.319 --> 00:06:16.279
Classmate Meiduo,

00:06:16.519 --> 00:06:17.519
you go first.

00:06:19.480 --> 00:06:20.279
I...

00:06:21.040 --> 00:06:23.959
Let's give classmate Meiduo a round of applause.

00:06:33.959 --> 00:06:35.279
Since I was little, I lived

00:06:35.800 --> 00:06:37.639
a life no different from cattle and sheep.

00:06:39.560 --> 00:06:40.759
Before I was 20,

00:06:41.639 --> 00:06:42.920
I never had a full meal.

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:45.639
As soon as I could hold a whip,

00:06:45.639 --> 00:06:47.279
I went to herd sheep for the lord.

00:06:48.439 --> 00:06:49.439
When I got a bit older,

00:06:50.439 --> 00:06:52.079
I was sent to Balu Mansion to be a household serf.

00:06:53.279 --> 00:06:54.759
Inside the high walls of Balu Mansion,

00:06:54.959 --> 00:06:56.959
the master lived in the tower in the center of the courtyard.

00:06:57.720 --> 00:07:01.240
A dozen of us household serfs huddled in the hay of the cowshed.

00:07:01.920 --> 00:07:03.160
Carrying water,

00:07:04.040 --> 00:07:05.399
scrubbing floors,

00:07:06.319 --> 00:07:07.480
feeding horses,

00:07:07.480 --> 00:07:09.439
getting beaten and scolded.

00:07:09.759 --> 00:07:11.560
When Mom got sick,

00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:13.920
there was no money for treatment.

00:07:15.319 --> 00:07:17.160
When Mom died,

00:07:18.480 --> 00:07:19.800
there was no money for a burial.

00:07:21.959 --> 00:07:23.199
Trampled upon,

00:07:23.560 --> 00:07:24.759
bought and sold at will,

00:07:25.839 --> 00:07:26.800
given away as gifts.

00:07:27.439 --> 00:07:29.399
The only difference from cattle and sheep

00:07:29.399 --> 00:07:31.560
was that we could speak.

00:07:31.920 --> 00:07:33.920
If I hadn't escaped with my sister,

00:07:35.279 --> 00:07:37.720
if the PLA hadn't saved us,

00:07:38.360 --> 00:07:40.199
and given us the chance to study

00:07:40.199 --> 00:07:42.600
and work,

00:07:43.759 --> 00:07:46.040
I wouldn't know

00:07:46.720 --> 00:07:49.000
what dignity,

00:07:49.000 --> 00:07:50.600
freedom,

00:07:50.600 --> 00:07:51.879
and equality are.

00:07:53.120 --> 00:07:55.639
I certainly wouldn't understand what ideals are.

00:08:02.279 --> 00:08:03.959
But now I have an ideal.

00:08:04.920 --> 00:08:06.680
That is to study hard,

00:08:07.160 --> 00:08:08.439
return to Xizang,

00:08:08.920 --> 00:08:11.240
and liberate more serfs like us.

00:08:11.879 --> 00:08:14.079
They are still in the straw nests by the animal pens,

00:08:14.079 --> 00:08:15.480
suffering,

00:08:15.480 --> 00:08:16.680
and being humiliated.

00:08:20.319 --> 00:08:21.680
I agree with what Meiduo said.

00:08:23.160 --> 00:08:25.360
We must return to Xizang as soon as possible

00:08:25.360 --> 00:08:26.439
to help more

00:08:26.439 --> 00:08:28.279
serfs like us,

00:08:29.319 --> 00:08:31.920
and let them live a good life.

00:08:40.320 --> 00:08:42.480
At our opening ceremony today,

00:08:42.759 --> 00:08:45.080
we have not only students from the Tibetan Public School

00:08:45.440 --> 00:08:47.159
but also students from the Tibetan Youth League School.

00:08:47.279 --> 00:08:48.279
From now on,

00:08:48.279 --> 00:08:50.360
we will all learn from each other.

00:08:50.720 --> 00:08:54.039
Especially the young ladies and masters from noble families,

00:08:54.159 --> 00:08:56.840
you must learn more from student Gesang,

00:08:56.840 --> 00:08:58.000
communicate more,

00:08:58.120 --> 00:09:00.720
and get rid of your pampered habits.

00:09:01.440 --> 00:09:03.360
Become self-reliant workers.

00:09:12.120 --> 00:09:12.919
Meiduo,

00:09:13.360 --> 00:09:14.519
what you said yesterday was great.

00:09:15.639 --> 00:09:17.320
I sent you to Shaanxi to study

00:09:17.559 --> 00:09:19.399
because right now in Xizang,

00:09:19.399 --> 00:09:21.159
it cannot yet hold a quiet desk.

00:09:22.440 --> 00:09:23.639
You must study hard,

00:09:23.759 --> 00:09:24.639
enrich yourself,

00:09:25.320 --> 00:09:26.639
and strive to soon

00:09:26.639 --> 00:09:27.759
return to Xizang

00:09:27.759 --> 00:09:28.879
to participate in management and construction.

00:09:29.559 --> 00:09:30.240
Yeah.

00:09:32.960 --> 00:09:34.000
Meiduo,

00:09:34.000 --> 00:09:35.320
there's something

00:09:35.320 --> 00:09:36.840
I want to ask your opinion on.

00:09:37.360 --> 00:09:38.919
What is it? Go ahead.

00:09:41.240 --> 00:09:42.440
I want to ask...

00:09:44.159 --> 00:09:44.960
I want...

00:09:46.759 --> 00:09:48.039
Meiduo,

00:09:48.960 --> 00:09:50.960
I actually want to ask you...

00:09:52.519 --> 00:09:53.320
Um,

00:09:58.240 --> 00:09:59.919
I want to go home tomorrow.

00:10:00.679 --> 00:10:02.200
Do you want to come with me?

00:10:03.720 --> 00:10:04.360
I...

00:10:07.519 --> 00:10:08.720
The wind blows,

00:10:08.720 --> 00:10:09.919
the wheels roll by,

00:10:10.279 --> 00:10:12.320
but I only hear my own heartbeat.

00:10:12.759 --> 00:10:15.320
His back as he rides is steadier than a snow mountain,

00:10:15.720 --> 00:10:18.639
while I hold wildflowers, sweating with nervousness.

00:10:19.440 --> 00:10:21.960
If only this road had no end.

00:10:22.159 --> 00:10:23.639
Just following him like this,

00:10:23.639 --> 00:10:24.720
through the waves of wheat,

00:10:24.919 --> 00:10:25.960
through the cooking smoke,

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:28.480
all the way to what I never dared to dream of before:

00:10:28.480 --> 00:10:29.840
the direction of home.

00:10:36.480 --> 00:10:37.240
We're here.

00:10:40.159 --> 00:10:40.840
Let's go.

00:10:43.960 --> 00:10:46.080
Is there anything I should mind when meeting your family?

00:10:46.080 --> 00:10:47.080
No need to mind anything.

00:10:47.080 --> 00:10:47.960
They are all very easygoing.

00:10:48.360 --> 00:10:49.159
Gao Yuan.

00:10:51.120 --> 00:10:51.919
Dad!